#  VS CODE
#  These files ARE committed — project config for everyone:
#    .vscode/extensions.json   → recommended extensions popup
#    .vscode/launch.json       → debug configurations (F5)
#    .vscode/tasks.json        → task runner shortcuts
#  Only personal/local settings are excluded:
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
